window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The official novelization of the summer blockbuster <i>The Predator</i>, Shane Black's new movie with a screenplay by Shane Black and Fred Dekker.</p> <p>The official novelization of the summer blockbuster <i>The Predator</i>, Shane Black's new movie set within the universe of the previous films. With a screenplay by Shane Black and Fred Dekker, the film stars Yvonne Strahovski, Boyd Holbrook, Olivia Munn, Alfie Allen, Thomas Jane, Sterling Brown, Keegan-Michael Key, Edward James Olmos, Jake Busey, and more. </p> <p>Author Christopher Golden (<i>Alien: River of Pain</i>) will work closely with James A. Moore, author for the official prequel novel.</p>"; 
